0.text: His brother and sister laughed at him. Next morning, he woke up at six o´clock. He started to pack a bag. He took some clothes out of the cupboard. He went to the kitchen. He took some sweets and a bottle of water. He went to the door. "Where are you going?" his mother asked. "To climb the Mount Everest," he said. "Alone?" "Yes," he said. "You´re a brave boy my dear. But you´re only seven."
